{ Matrix operations #matrix-operations

  Matrix transposition: → development/languages/R/functions/t[t()]

  Matrix inverse: → development/languages/R/functions/solve[solve()]

  Matrix multiplication: `m1 %*% m2` (`m1 * m2` is an element wise operation).

  n*n diagonal (identity) matrix: → development/languages/R/functions/diag[diag()]

